2007-03-17 21:12  jannis

	* modules/menu/menu-data/Makefile.am,
	  modules/menu/menu-data/about-xfce.desktop,
	  modules/menu/menu-data/file-manager.desktop,
	  modules/menu/menu-data/help.desktop,
	  modules/menu/menu-data/logout.desktop,
	  modules/menu/menu-data/run-program.desktop,
	  modules/menu/menu-data/terminal.desktop,
	  modules/menu/menu-data/web-browser.desktop,
	  modules/menu/menu-data/xfce-applications.menu.in,
	  modules/menu/menu-data/xfce4-about-xfce.desktop,
	  modules/menu/menu-data/xfce4-file-manager.desktop,
	  modules/menu/menu-data/xfce4-help.desktop,
	  modules/menu/menu-data/xfce4-logout.desktop,
	  modules/menu/menu-data/xfce4-run-program.desktop,
	  modules/menu/menu-data/xfce4-terminal.desktop,
	  modules/menu/menu-data/xfce4-web-browser.desktop:
	  All .desktop files now have a "xfce4-" prefix, are part of the
	  "X-Xfce-Toplevel" category and OnlyShowIn=XFCE. They're not
	  installed into /usr/share/applications/menu-data/ anymore.
	  
	  Added a <Layout> element to xfce-applications.menu.in. Also
	  cleaned
	  up the file a little and added an <Include> rule for the
	  "X-Xfce-Toplevel" category in the root menu element.

2007-03-04 07:18  erenturkay

	* po/tr.po:
	  update Turkish translation

2007-03-03 10:06  mvd

	* po/ChangeLog, po/uk.po:
	  2007-03-03 Maxim Dziumanenko <dziumanenko@gmail.com>
	  
	  * Update Ukrainian translation.

2007-02-25 02:28  kelnos

	* settings/appearance-settings.c:
	  fix uri parsing to unescape '%##' stuff in the uri (bug 2942)

2007-02-25 01:37  kelnos

	* src/xfce-backdrop.c:
	  use nearest-neighbor interpolation when compositing a backdrop
	  image when the
	  image src is just centered or tiled onto dest. using bilinear or
	  hyper interp
	  causes blurriness in those cases. (patch mostly from Henk Boom,
	  bug 2939).
	  
	  also, a minor optimisation: if the src and dest image sizes are
	  equal, pretend
	  the image style is 'centered' regardless of whatever it is to
	  avoid extra
	  scaling or pixbuf copying.

2007-02-22 17:51  kelnos

	* configure.ac.in, modules/menu/menu-data/Makefile.am,
	  modules/menu/menu-data/xfce-applications.menu.in:
	  fix weirdness with $prefix and expand $datadir properly

