2006-11-09 19:58  kelnos

	* README, src/xfce-desktop.c:
	  * move removable icon enable call to after special icon so
	  special icons show
	  up first
	  * add hidden options to enable/disable removable icons and the 3
	  special icons.
	  yeah, i know, but it's a very very small, low-risk change, and
	  people will
	  appreciate it.

2006-11-09 07:47  kelnos

	* configure.ac.in:
	  * add a verbose warning message when dbus or thunar-vfs can't be
	  found
	  (bug 2522)
	  * move all required version numbers to the top of
	  configure.ac.in to make
	  changing them easy

2006-11-06 07:39  kelnos

	* src/xfdesktop-icon-view.c:
	  fix < vs. >= typo :-P

2006-11-06 07:16  kelnos

	* src/xfdesktop-icon-view.c:
	  * remove spurious 'realized' check in
	  xfdesktop_icon_view_remove_all(), as
	  there are never icons in priv->icons if the icon view is not
	  realized
	  * handle internal movements of icons between priv->icons and
	  priv->pending_icons
	  much saner, by separating out the actual addition to
	  priv->icons. this has
	  the nice result that icons don't disappear completely (and thus
	  leak memory)
	  if the icon size is set such that there isn't enough room on the
	  desktop for
	  a particular icon. if the icon size is later set smaller such
	  that the icon
	  will now fit, it'll reappear properly on its own (bug 1546)

2006-11-06 06:14  kelnos

	* src/xfdesktop-icon-view.c:
	  change icon cell sizing to be pix size * 2.5. this should
	  mitigate some of
	  the weirdness in bug 1546, though icons will still disappear if
	  you make
	  the icon size too large to fit all icons on the desktop. getting
	  the icons
	  back means dropping the icon size down, and then manually
	  refreshing the
	  desktop with F5. that's just how it is.

2006-11-06 02:37  kelnos

	* settings/appearance-settings.c, xfdesktop.spec.in:
	  correct typo

2006-11-06 00:51  kelnos

	* src/xfce-desktop.c:
	  reset the root window's back pixmap and those magic window
	  properties when
	  the backdrop changes. this fixes apps like terminal and xchat
	  not updating
	  their background when they do their pseudo-transparency thing
	  (bug 2508)

2006-11-05 18:54  paurullan

	* po/ChangeLog, po/ko.po:
	  i18n Korean update

