2006-10-19 02:39  kelnos

	* src/xfdesktop-file-icon.c, src/xfdesktop-file-icon.h,
	  src/xfdesktop-icon.c, src/xfdesktop-icon.h,
	  src/xfdesktop-regular-file-icon.c,
	  src/xfdesktop-special-file-icon.c, src/xfdesktop-volume-icon.c,
	  src/xfdesktop-window-icon.c, src/xfdesktop-window-icon.h:
	  * XfdesktopIcon is no longer a GTypeInterface; it's now just a
	  normal GType
	  (well, an abstract one).
	  * moved the _get/set_extents() and _get/set_position() stuff
	  into XfdesktopIcon
	  and removed the duplicated code in XfdesktopFileIcon and
	  XfdesktopWindowIcon

