2006-02-06 09:20  kelnos

	* src/xfdesktop-icon-view.c, src/xfdesktop-icon-view.h,
	  src/xfdesktop-window-icon-manager.c:
	  ok, that was wrong. handle icon selection by adding some signals
	  to
	  XfdesktopIconView. it's more efficient this way anyway, since
	  it's one signal
	  per view instead of per icon

2006-02-06 09:07  kelnos

	* src/xfdesktop-window-icon-manager.c,
	  src/xfdesktop-window-icon.c, src/xfdesktop-window-icon.h:
	  * fix crash; each icon_workspaces[] element will always be valid
	  now
