2005-08-16 10:33  kelnos

	* settings/backdrop_settings.c, settings/settings_common.h,
	  src/xfce-desktop.c:
	  add option to stretch backdrop across all xinerama screens (bug
	  727)
	  limitations:
	  * only works with xinerama (no standard multiscreen).
	  * will likely look pretty funny if the resolution isn't the same
	  on all
	  monitors.
	  * will break if it ever becomes possible to change xinerama
	  config without
	  restarting X, or you can have mixed multiscreen/xinerama.
	  i should be sleeping.

